    175          /**
    176           * Add a new Log Message to the Message Queue.
    177           *
    178           * Log Messages that are disabled through a filter will not be added to the Message Queue.
    179           *
    180           * If the Message Queue is full when this function is called, then the passed information will be
    181           * discarded. The alternative solution of dropping the oldest Log Message is not used. If a
    182           * project module floods the Message Queue, the Log Messages leading up to the flood are typically
    183           * more useful than the repeated Log Message that generates the flood.
